metadata.name: Hawksbill Blue
metadata.description:
"Hawksbill Blue" 

BURN TO REDEEM

*Burn 2x "Hawksbill Blue" to get 1x " A Turtle's Trail" 

------------------------------------------------------------

*Every Hawksbill Blue piece minted counts as a raffle ticket to a new never seen before coral edition piece <3  (The more mints the merrier )

*Holding Both edition counts as a raffle tickets for a 1 of 1 marinelife image <3 (Max 1 entry) 

------------------------------------------------------------

This image captures the serene beauty of a Hawksbill turtle as it gracefully swims through the crystal clear waters of the Red Sea, Sharm el sheik, Egypt .  

A sharksucker is catching a free ride on the Turtles shell

The deep blue color of the water adds a sense of tranquility and peace to the image ,while the turtle itself is a symbol of grace and strength.

Own a touch of the natural world into your collection. serving as a reminder of the beauty and importance of the oceans & all marine life 

Own a piece of the Red Sea's natural beauty. My story & my Ocean explorations of our oceans & marine life below the waves. 

*Production price for anyone holding either of these piece & wants to have it printed for their home or office included! 

Thank you! for your interest.
